com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport
Class ItemIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.ItemIdentifier

public final class ItemIdentifier
extends Object

A container for the unique identifier of an Item that does not also include version information.

An ItemIdentifier also contains an identifier for the Item's originating data source.

Since:
1.0
